name: What Is Thy Bidding, My Master?
Lore: 'Reaching across the galaxy, the Emperor uses his vast powers to require immediate submission and obedience. His minions frequently find this inconvenient.',
Text: 'Deploy on Emperor or any system. Target one character whose lore uses the word ''Emperor.'' Target cannot use ability to draw battle destiny and is excluded from being the ''highest-ability character.'' Utinni Effect canceled when reached by target.',
